title: Assigned covered parking, Sparkling swimming pool with sun deck & BBQ
posting_body: ['Welcome to Pleasanton Heights Apartment Homes!', 'Pleasanton Heights is a beautiful community nestled in a residential neighborhood within walking distance to downtown Pleasanton, where restaurants, boutiques, and one of a kind shops line the streets.', "On Friday nights, enjoy Free Concerts in the Park; every Saturday, shop the Farmer's Market; and throughout the year, enjoy a variety of fun-filled activities.", 'The apartment homes at Pleasanton Heights have been upgraded with granite countertops, Whirlpool stainless steel appliances, and plank flooring on ground level units (bedrooms are carpeted).', '- Sparkling swimming pool with sun deck', '- 24 hours on-site laundry facility', '- Relaxing garden walkways', '- Professional management & maintenance team', '- Assigned covered parking', '- Award winning Pleasanton School District', '- Barbecue/Lounge Area', '- Public transportation nearby', '- Blocks from historical Downtown Pleasanton', '- Beautiful views of the Pleasanton Hills and Mt. Diablo', '- Many options to pay rent including, credit card, on-line and ACH', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', 'Pricing is subject to change.', 'Call for details.']
